{"id":"1a499711-ddd6-4b82-9200-549447524238","name":"Gabriel Miller | ROCKSTAR","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Your baby-daddy still dreams of being a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>rockstar</strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">!?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_d34e6211-5cf1-4d00-9a6e-1e4ee2cb9199.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"Oh, you just got to be up high where the whole world is watching me cause I...I got the guts to be <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6w8dBm5KlXxWejYrbGS1EJ?si=tpd2F5-TS9Wohif1X4RlxA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong><em>somebody</em></strong></span></a>!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_66ec2661-1249-4e81-89b3-a672ae1f0bb1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ Gabe’s always dreamed of being a <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>rockstar</strong></span>, and well… technically, he is! Some of his tracks still get played on those old radio stations late at night, so that’s something, right?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Gabe is always off somewhere with his guitar, acting like he’s still living in the glory days. He’s got a heart of gold, sure, but <span style=\"color: #a11313\"><strong>responsibility</strong></span>? Nah. He'd rather be on stage, even if it's just in his head.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>Unfortunately</strong></span> for you, this massive idiot happens to be the <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>father</strong></span> of your daughter. Time for him to grow up, innit?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_cde1a4d4-8fc7-4dda-82d6-05e0212b96dd.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #891b1b; color: inherit\">☆ TW: sfw intro, ANY POV (but it’s implied user went through a pregnancy), pathetic man asking for money alert!, established relationship (you’re co-parenting, not in a romantic relationship), no major warnings.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_38b83718-f886-4a9d-ae0a-0b2b2cf26735.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ Gabe is here! Writing him was a blast, especially since <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/d6c28c78-675c-42d4-953f-2b9fa7ec5958_profile-of-mocha-mochi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>Mocha</strong></span></a> helped me brainstorm and flesh out his backstory (he was originally just gonna be your deadbeat boyfriend, but we def need more dilfs in this site, cough) so everyone say <strong><mark style=\"background-color: #891b1b; color: inherit\">thanks Momo!</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ psst… did you know I have a <a href=\"https://discord.gg/T89cNJCHqN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>server</strong></span></a>? Just saying! There’s a cute girl named <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/2cc5e3ca-ec9c-452f-a484-6e71f35176da_profile-of-silkbabey\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 27, 27)\"><strong>Rosie</strong></span></a> as the admin there (leaning on my mansion).</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ next bot: clingy emo bf! 🦭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_40e6af","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_6a1bf7b7-e9d2-4290-b799-02b6d19e796a.webp","creator":"dellya_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":7699,"messages":136471,"created_at":"2024-09-24T23:14:13.774107+00:00"}